## Proposed Changes

### [Component 1] Core Bug Fixes & Refactoring

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///e:/Google%20Hackathon/Google-AI-Seekho-Hackathon-/main.py)
* Add the missing `/api/dispute` HTTP POST endpoint so that the DisputeAgent can be independently queried and tested by both the test runner and the Flutter frontend.

#### [MODIFY] [firebase_client.py](file:///e:/Google%20Hackathon/Google-AI-Seekho-Hackathon-/database/firebase_client.py)
* Rewrite `get_last_job` to query for the provider's jobs and sort them in Python memory, preventing crashing due to missing Firestore composite indexes.

#### [MODIFY] [discovery_agent.py](file:///e:/Google%20Hackathon/Google-AI-Seekho-Hackathon-/agents/discovery_agent.py)
* Fix `_filter_by_radius` to correctly match the seeded provider IDs (`prv_ac_1`, `prv_ac_2`, etc.) and calculate distance dynamically based on user coordinate proximity.

---

### [Component 2] Dedicated Test Scenarios Suite

#### [NEW] [test_agents.py](file:///e:/Google%20Hackathon/Google-AI-Seekho-Hackathon-/test_scenarios/test_agents.py)
* Individual unit/integration tests for each of the 10 agents in isolation to verify status outputs, intent parses, and pricing breakdown correctness.

#### [NEW] [test_connection.py](file:///e:/Google%20Hackathon/Google-AI-Seekho-Hackathon-/test_scenarios/test_connection.py)
* Verifies that the FastAPI routes (`/api/request`, `/api/dispute`, `/ws/trace`) are fully operational and reachable.

#### [NEW] [test_runner.py](file:///e:/Google%20Hackathon/Google-AI-Seekho-Hackathon-/test_scenarios/test_runner.py)
* Consolidated script that runs all test scenarios sequentially and outputs a beautiful, readable terminal report.

#### [DELETE] [test_scenarios.py](file:///e:/Google%20Hackathon/Google-AI-Seekho-Hackathon-/test_scenarios.py)
* Delete the outdated, top-level testing script.

