## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
* Run `python -m test_scenarios.test_runner` to execute all tests:
  * Unit tests for each of the 10 agents
  * REST API tests (`/api/request` & `/api/dispute`)
  * Live WebSockets trace streams (`/ws/trace`)
* Confirm all tests return green and database reads/writes occur without exceptions.

### Manual Verification
* Ensure the FastAPI reload log is clean.
* Send an ambiguity location request (`DHA`) to verify the geo-normalization halt loop is working properly.
* Send a rating of `1` or `2` to verify the dispute resolution pipeline triggers seamlessly.
